    <!-- content to be displayed at strategy screen -->
    <string name="st_title">Keep calm and learn japanese !</string>
    <string name="app_desc">Parrot Japanese application is designed for the beginners and the speaking-oriented Japanese learners or who need to be familiar with Japanese in a very short time. It is useful to use this app as a small dictionary. For the beginners, following guidance to help using this app effectively:</string>
    <string-array name="st_steps">
        <item>Japanese alphabet: Hiragana and Katakana</item>
        <item>Learn vocabulary: Essential vocabulary and Count numbers</item>
        <item>Exercises</item>
        <item>Learn basic grammar</item>
        <item>Learn daily life simple phrases</item>
        <item>Goto next level</item>
    </string-array>

    <string-array name="st_targets">
        <item>First step for you familiar with basic Japanese sounds and characters. You will remember them automatically when you go through other steps. So you should not waste weeks or a month to remember all of them before going to next steps.</item>
        <item>Take a few days or a week to take a look on all words once. You will come back here many times when necessary.</item>
        <item>Check your vocabulary with exercises</item>
        <item>Video series made by Japanese native speaker to help you learn simple Japanese grammar. These videos teach you to speak a sentence from very simple to complicated.</item>
        <item>Common use phrases which are not in grammar videos</item>
        <item>Learn more vocabulary, grammar, listening and writing skills from recommended resources</item>
    </string-array>
    <string name="st_goodbye">Have a good time!</string>
    <!-- end strategy screen -->


